{
  "text": "The trajectory of all simulations was evaluated by calculating root mean square deviations (RMSD) for the lid backbone using both structure (close and open state) as reference and analyzed with visual molecular dynamics (VMD) program version 1.9.1 [CITATION_1] . Root mean square deviation (RMSD) was measured for position of particle with respect to reference position over time 17 . RMSD is calculated by the following formula:",
